{{Infobox dungeon |name = Warm-Up Tunnel |image = [[File:Warm-Up Tunnel.png|thumb]] |caption = A map of Warm-Up Tunnel. |tokens = 1,730,000 |location = Between Training Lowlands and Potbottom Desert }} '''Warm-Up Tunnel''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Galar]]. It initially has 125 tiles arranged in two floors: 10x10 and 6x6 in size, respectively; including 16 chest tiles, 38 non-boss encounter tiles, 1 ladder tile, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 28,252,100 HP.
